obtaining.description: Whenever a block is broken or otherwise disappears, a block of air replaces it.
Using an undamaged anvil or dropping it has a chance of turning it into this.
Using an slightly damaged anvil or dropping it has a chance of turning it into this.
12 blocks of bedrock generate as part of each End gateway. Two linked End gateways generate each time an Ender dragon is killed. Up to 20 pairs of gateways can be generated.
End return portals which look like End gateways are randomly generated in the End. 12 blocks of bedrock generate as part of each.
One chest generates near the spawn of any world that has the bonus chest option enabled.
White concrete powder solidifies into white concrete when next to water.
Orange concrete powder solidifies into orange concrete when next to water.
Purple concrete powder solidifies into purple concrete when next to water.
Blue concrete powder solidifies into blue concrete when next to water.
Brown concrete powder solidifies into brown concrete when next to water.
Green concrete powder solidifies into green concrete when next to water.
Red concrete powder solidifies into red concrete when next to water.
Black concrete powder solidifies into black concrete when next to water.
Magenta concrete powder solidifies into magenta concrete when next to water.
Light blue concrete powder solidifies into light blue concrete when next to water.
Yellow concrete powder solidifies into yellow concrete when next to water.
Lime concrete powder solidifies into lime concrete when next to water.
Pink concrete powder solidifies into pink concrete when next to water.
Gray concrete powder solidifies into gray concrete when next to water.
Light gray concrete powder solidifies into light gray concrete when next to water.
Cyan concrete powder solidifies into cyan concrete when next to water.
Farmland will turn into dirt if either a mob jumps on it, or if nothing is planted on it and it is not within four blocks of water.
Grass, mycelium, podzol, farmland, and grass paths turn into dirt over time when a solid block is located directly above them.
Glass bottles can be converted to dragon's breath by using them on areas affected by the Ender dragon's breath attack.
One dragon egg generates on top of the End exit portal when the first Ender dragon is killed.
A chicken will lay an egg once every 6–12 in-game hours (5–10 minutes).
Two linked End gateways generate each time an Ender dragon is killed. Up to 20 gateways can be generated.
End return portals which look like End gateways are randomly generated in the End.
16 blocks of End stone generate directly under the edge of the End exit portal each time an Ender dragon is spawned or killed.
Fire can be created by flint & steel, lightning, lava, explosions, or other blocks of fire.
Frosted ice is generated by players walking near water while wearing boots with the Frost Walker enchantment.
In locations with cold enough temperatures and a light level of 11 or lower, water will freeze into ice.
The iron bars around some of the Ender crystals regenerate every time an Ender dragon is spawned.

long_fire_resistance.name: Lingering Potion of Fire Resistance, extended

long_night_vision.name: Lingering Potion of Night Vision, extended

long_water_breathing.name: Lingering Potion of Water Breathing, extended

obtaining.description: An unlit redstone lamp will turn into this when redstone-powered.
14 blocks of obsidian generate as part of a Nether portal when an unlinked portal is used.
25 blocks of obsidian generate as part of the End spawn platform each time an entity enters the End. This allows for automatic farming as shown in this video.
The obsidian pillars in the End regenerate every time an Ender dragon is spawned.
A piston or sticky piston will produce one of these when it becomes redstone-powered. The block goes away when the signal is removed.
An unpowered repeater will turn into this when it becomes powered by a redstone signal from its rear input.
During snowfall, a layer of snow can generate on top of solid blocks with a block light level 10 or less, with the exception of packed ice.
In some biomes, snow golems generate a trail of snow where they walk.

long_fire_resistance.name: Splash Potion of Fire Resistance, extended

long_night_vision.name: Splash Potion of Night Vision, extended

long_water_breathing.name: Splash Potion of Water Breathing, extended

obtaining.description: When water touches a dry sponge, it will turn into this and absorb the water.
Up to 4 torches generate around the bonus chest if the corresponding option is enabled.
This block is created when a sign is placed against another block horizontally.
